Emit the anchored key-prefix filter lists an external replication service needs for one (database, target)

Usage: sleet mirror prefixes --format <FORMAT> <ROOT> <DB> <TARGET>

Arguments:
  <ROOT>
          Fleet root URL, e.g. s3://ops/sleet/

  <DB>
          Registered database URL

  <TARGET>
          Mirror target name

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>
          Which service's configuration shape to emit

          Possible values:
          - s3:    S3 bucket replication rules
          - sts:   GCS Storage Transfer Service include prefixes
          - azure: Azure object replication rules

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
